headline: ICE First Look at Mortgage Performance: Delinquencies Hit Highest Level in Nearly Three Years; Prepayments Drop on Higher Rates
summary: ATLANTA & NEW YORK, December 23, 2024--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE:ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, reports the following "first look" at November 2024 month-end mortgage performance statistics derived from its loan-level database representing the majority of the national mortgage market.
